Title: The Misguided  Path of a 23 yr old Virgin
DateModified: '2019-02-20'
DatePublished: '2019-02-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/the-misguided-path-of-a-23-yr-old-virgin
SetInCountry: Usa
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Mylisyaa Sefu
AuthorCountry: United States of America
Text: "Growing up in a generation where sex is no longer a privilege but a pressured\
  \ obligation. Young 23 yr old Mali struggles to find love & romance while navigating\
  \ through College, Work and life. All the While trying to find herself and the woman\
  \ she wants to be through experiences & lessons from  Men, friends and family which\
  \ leaves her as confused as ever.   When dating her bows continue to consistently\
  \ bore her & it turns into a predictive cycle she wonders is sex the answer? The\
  \ missing key?  Is that why all her conquests for love and romance fails? & if it\
  \ is the answer which bow should it be with? They all have one thing she adores\
  \ immensely but she can\u2019t find it all in one. This takes her on numerous adventures\
  \ & embarrassing moments. Mali contemplates dropping them all and focusing on her\
  \ Traveling career, but even then who wants to travel alone, when the world awaits."
